Class CreditCardOverride

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.netradius.protectpay.CreditCardOverride
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class CreditCardOverride
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Holds credit card override values. These values will override the values on a payment method when used to make a payment.
